Welcome
-------

zdevices is the ZeroMQ devices collection, a repository of device packages
written by and for ZeroMQ users.  All code is GPLv3 licensed.

Building and installation instructions are provided with each package.

zdevices is organized by language.

Resources
---------

zdevices is developed by and for the ZeroMQ community.

Websites: http://www.zeromq.org/docs:zdevices

Development mailing list: zeromq-dev@lists.zeromq.org
Announcements mailing list: zeromq-announce@lists.zeromq.org

Git repository: http://github.com/imatix/zdevices

ZeroMQ developers can also be found on the IRC channel #zeromq, on the
Freenode network (irc.freenode.net).

Contributions
-------------

See the BYLAWS file included with the distribution.

